headline: BTQ Technologies Begins Trading on Nasdaq
summary: BTQ Technologies Corp. (the "Company" or "BTQ") (Nasdaq: BTQ) (CBOE CA: BTQ) (FSE: NG3), a global quantum technology company focused on securing mission-critical networks, is pleased to announce that its common shares (the "Common Shares") will begin trading today on the Nasdaq Global Market ("Nasdaq") under the symbol "BTQ".
